config BR2_PACKAGE_PI_BLASTER
    bool "pi-blaster"
    depends on BR2_LINUX_KERNEL_DEFCONFIG = "bcm2709"
    help
        This project enables PWM on the GPIO pins you request
        of a Raspberry Pi. The technique used is extremely 
        efficient: does not use the CPU and gives very stable pulses.

        https://github.com/sarfata/pi-blaster
